No. 391,

Misc.

Swift v. Commandant, U. S. Disciplinary Barracks, Fort Leavenworth. Solicitor General Griswold, Assistant Attorney General Wilson, Jerome M. Feit, and Roger A. Pauley for respondent.

C. A. 10th Cir. Certiorari denied.

Mr. Justice Douglas is of the opinion that certiorari should be granted.
